ESHRE guideline: medically assisted reproduction in patients with a viral 
infection/disease.

ESHRE Guideline Group on Viral infection/disease; Mocanu E(1), Drakeley A(2), 
Kupka MS(3), Lara-Molina EE(4), Le Clef N(5), Ombelet W(6), Patrat C(7), 
Pennings G(8), Semprini AE(9), Tilleman K(10), Tognon M(11), Tonch N(12), 
