Valorisation of fruit peel bioactive into green synthesized silver nanoparticles 
to modify cellulose wrapper for shelf-life extension of packaged bread.

Gopalakrishnan K(1), Chandel M(2), Gupta V(1), Kaur K(1), Patel A(3), Kaur K(2), 
Kishore A(1), Prabhakar PK(1), Singh A(1), Shankar Prasad J(1), Bodana V(1), 
